description: Jura Energy Corporation engages in the development, exploration, and production of oil and gas properties. It holds working interests in three exploration licenses, including Guddu, Zamzama North, and Nareli; and six leases comprising Reti, Maru, Maru South, Zarghun South, Sara, and Suri covering a total area of 5998.99 square kilometers located at various basins in Pakistan. The company is headquartered in Calgary, Canada. Jura Energy Corporation is a subsidiary of JS Energy Limited.
